From 50c9eafea298239ecc193aeb2015cccacf87fc5d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harsh Kumar Bijlani <quic_hbijlani@quicinc.com>
Date: Wed, 26 Mar 2025 18:22:01 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: ath12k: Move link stats from CP Object

As part of peer modularization in Unified Driver Framework, the station
view is as follows:
            Common Path                      Data Path
    -------------------------------------------------------------------
    ath12k_sta                           ath12k_dp_peer
        |                                       |
        |-> ath12k_link_sta    <---->           |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer
        |                                       |
        |-> ath12k_link_sta    <---->           |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer
        |                                       |
        |-> ath12k_link_sta    <---->           |-> ath12k_dp_link_peer

Currently ath12k_link_sta has data path stats updated in tx_htt and rx
monitor path. This patch is to move those stats from ath12_link_sta to
ath12k_dp_link_peer to align with peer modularization model as shown
above.

This patch also includes new API:
	ath12k_link_peer_get_sta_rate_info_stats()
API is a wrapper API to fill the various link_peer stats into an object
of 'struct ath12k_dp_link_peer_rate_info'.

Signed-off-by: Harsh Kumar Bijlani <quic_hbijlani@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Ripan Deuri <quic_rdeuri@quicinc.com>
